\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
\begin{document}
}{}$12.9~\mu \text {g/m}^{3}$
\end{document} in 367 cities of China [87]. It is also reported that PM2.5 was reduced by \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
\usepackage{amsmath}
\usepackage{wasysym} 
\usepackage{amsfonts} 
\usepackage{amssymb} 
\usepackage{amsbsy}
\usepackage{upgreek}
\usepackage{mathrsfs}
